# Enterprise Content Governance Framework

## Objective

Ensure enterprise content is accurate, discoverable, consistent, accessible, and measurable throughout its lifecycle.

---

## Content Lifecycle

```text
Business Request
        ↓
Planning
        ↓
Research
        ↓
Content Creation
        ↓
Editorial Review
        ↓
SME Validation
        ↓
Compliance Review
        ↓
Metadata Assignment
        ↓
Publishing
        ↓
Quality Assurance
        ↓
Analytics & Reporting
        ↓
Continuous Improvement
```

---

## Governance Principles

- Accuracy
- Consistency
- Accessibility
- Metadata Integrity
- Brand Alignment
- Regulatory Compliance
- Content Discoverability
- Continuous Improvement
